originalText.text: Fiona O Azubuike is one of the rudest most obnoxious doctors encountered in an emergency setting.  She feels no need to introduce herself and is beyond arrogant. If you have her as an attending physician at Mt. Sinai - you will experience her unprofessional nature first hand.

originalText.text: Something is seriously wrong with this woman! She is the worst ER Doctor at Mount Sinai! Not only does she talk very loud an rude, she does not care! She sent me home only for me to return less than  24hrs an be rushed to emergency surgery by another Doctor! Fiona Azubuike you have failed me and I plan to tell the world about my experience in hopes that they never encounter your services!
